article_title: All systems go, but validating concept, gaining traction come first
article_text:
Challenge Champion Room2Care pushing forward with plan to disrupt a traditional senior-care industry

Second-place winner Wuelto, aims at giving small businesses in Latin America more visibility online, proving popular with users

Third-place winner Senzu Foods had plan to introduce Americans to insect-based foods

People’s Pick winner Court Buddy, a legal matching service, launches in 13 states and Washington, D.C.
